     Greetings.  I came out of the tunnel into DL and sought you out to see about joining up with your raid.  I am, as most paladins are, looking for the pally books needed for our epic quest.  After offering my assistance, I was told by you, and I quote, &quot;Too low, bud.&quot; <br>
